data.description: Built in 2008 this home contains almost 2900 sqft. of living space and a huge yard spanning three lots. Sounds like the spacious and desirable property you've been waiting for. The home boasts a three-car attached garage that is insulated to keep your cars warm during those cold winters. No more scraping snow and Ice off the windshield. Both the house and garage are insulated with spray foam. This type of insulation can help with energy efficiency, reducing heat loss and lowering utility costs. The covered front porch adds curb appeal and can be a great place to relax or socialize outdoors. The kitchen features Kraft Maid custom wood cabinets, which are known for their quality and durability. The kitchen appliances are brand new and are included with the house. The addition of granite countertops and ceramic tile floors adds a touch of elegance and practicality to the space. A built in bar with sink and fridge is perfect when entertaining guests.
